Use GrabzIt to take PDF or image screenshots of websites. The screenshots are highly customizable options include altering quality, delay, size, browser type, geographic location and much more.
Or capture tables from web pages and convert them into a CSV, JSON or Excel documents.
Additionally you can even convert online video's into animated GIF's.
